  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Katana Dragon</strong> is an <strong>action-RPG adventure and dungeons exploration</strong>, where you play as the ninjas Shin and Nobi in their quest to end the curse that hangs over Sogen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn ninja skills, upgrade your Dragon Gems, equip the Cursed Seals and level up. Avoid traps, solve puzzles and fight powerful enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your ninja way begins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE A VAST WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/0975bea21891b0783a5b07e14bb27a44.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/0975bea21891b0783a5b07e14bb27a44.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The beautiful lands of Sogen</strong> are waiting to be discovered. The whole map, their secrets, the challenges and even the dungeons have been <strong>hand designed</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MASTER NINJA SKILLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/b65bfaef47b7f1f4316401a97911be82.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/b65bfaef47b7f1f4316401a97911be82.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Learn new ninja skills</strong> that will help you solve puzzles, defeat enemies and even reach new areas and discover their secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT AGAINST ENEMIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/9ac8deb39454f8f5b10cfaf77b8fff60.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/9ac8deb39454f8f5b10cfaf77b8fff60.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight against Gokais</strong>, powerful creatures capable of breathing fire, biting or even flying. Will you be able to register them all in your <i>Gokairium</i>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DIVE INTO DUNGEONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/27599f53194885a8c055b8855246df42.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/27599f53194885a8c055b8855246df42.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore dungeons, wells and caves</strong> to find treasures and test your training. Walk through rooms, avoid their traps, and fight against <strong>bosses </strong>in epic battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR LOOK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/c0259652d30f8602ecf2e379b469d373.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Change your appearance</strong> with different outfits: kimonos, armors, hats, masks, dresses and much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EQUIP & UPGRADE YOUR DRAGON GEMS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/cd833d1f0cd22aa1d0d4395b015231ed.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boost your stats</strong> using the power contained in<strong> Dragon Gems</strong>. Get them in different forms, sets, and rarities to suit your combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEWARE WITH CURSED SEALS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/efb20a39659b8323cada821b4318ceee.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cursed Seals</strong> are powerful but dangerous items which you can benefit from their power as you deal with their <strong>curse</strong>. No pain, no gain!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Katana Dragon</strong> is an <strong>action-RPG adventure and dungeons exploration</strong>, where you play as the ninjas Shin and Nobi in their quest to end the curse that hangs over Sogen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn ninja skills, upgrade your Dragon Gems, equip the Cursed Seals and level up. Avoid traps, solve puzzles and fight powerful enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your ninja way begins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE A VAST WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/0975bea21891b0783a5b07e14bb27a44.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/0975bea21891b0783a5b07e14bb27a44.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The beautiful lands of Sogen</strong> are waiting to be discovered. The whole map, their secrets, the challenges and even the dungeons have been <strong>hand designed</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MASTER NINJA SKILLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/b65bfaef47b7f1f4316401a97911be82.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/b65bfaef47b7f1f4316401a97911be82.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Learn new ninja skills</strong> that will help you solv