73.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Change your appearance</strong> with different outfits: kimonos, armors, hats, masks, dresses and much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EQUIP & UPGRADE YOUR DRAGON GEMS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/cd833d1f0cd22aa1d0d4395b015231ed.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boost your stats</strong> using the power contained in<strong> Dragon Gems</strong>. Get them in different forms, sets, and rarities to suit your combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEWARE WITH CURSED SEALS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/efb20a39659b8323cada821b4318ceee.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cursed Seals</strong> are powerful but dangerous items which you can benefit from their power as you deal with their <strong>curse</strong>. No pain, no gain!</p>",
